<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
    <meta name="generator" content={Astro.generator} />
    <title>Maehe - 子育てツール集</title>
    <meta
      name="description"
      content="子育てをもっと便利に。習い事の予定管理などの便利ツールを集めました。"
    />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
    <link
      href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+JP:wght@400;500;600;700;900&family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;900&display=swap"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
    <style>
      :root {
        --primary: #6c63ff;
        --primary-light: #ece9ff;
        --text: #1e1b4b;
        --text-muted: #64748b;
        --text-faint: #94a3b8;
        --bg: #f0f4ff;
        --card: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.88);
        --card-border: rgba(108, 99, 255, 0.14);
        --font: "Noto Sans JP", "Inter", sans-serif;
        --ease: 0.22s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
      }
      *,
      *::before,
      *::after {
        box-sizing: border-box;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
      }
      body {
        font-family: var(--font);
        background: var(--bg);
        color: var(--text);
        min-height: 100vh;
        overflow-x: hidden;
      }

      /* Animated background blobs */
      .bg {
        position: fixed;
        inset: 0;
        z-index: 0;
        overflow: hidden;
        pointer-events: none;
      }
      .blob {
        position: absolute;
        border-radius: 50%;
        filter: blur(100px);
        animation: drift 18s ease-in-out infinite;
      }
      .blob-1 {
        width: 600px;
        height: 600px;
        background: radial-gradient(#a78bfa, #6c63ff);
        opacity: 0.4;
        top: -200px;
        right: -150px;
      }
      .blob-2 {
        width: 500px;
        height: 500px;
        background: radial-gradient(#43cbff, #7b2fff);
        opacity: 0.35;
        bottom: -100px;
        left: -100px;
        animation-delay: -7s;
      }
      .blob-3 {
        width: 350px;
        height: 350px;
        background: radial-gradient(#ff6584, #ffbe76);
        opacity: 0.3;
        top: 50%;
        left: 45%;
        animation-delay: -13s;
      }
      @keyframes drift {
        0%,
        100% {
          transform: translate(0, 0) scale(1);
        }
        33% {
          transform: translate(30px, -40px) scale(1.05);
        }
        66% {
          transform: translate(-20px, 20px) scale(0.97);
        }
      }

      /* Layout */
      .wrapper {
        position: relative;
        z-index: 1;
        min-height: 100vh;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
      }

      /* Hero */
      .hero {
        padding: 72px 24px 52px;
        text-align: center;
      }
      .badge {
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 8px;
        background: rgba(108, 99, 255, 0.12);
        border: 1.5px solid rgba(108, 99, 255, 0.2);
        color: var(--primary);
        font-size: 0.78rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        padding: 6px 16px;
        border-radius: 100px;
        margin-bottom: 24px;
      }
      .hero h1 {
        font-size: clamp(2.2rem, 6vw, 3.8rem);
        font-weight: 900;
        line-height: 1.15;
        letter-spacing: -1.5px;
        background: linear-gradient(
          135deg,
          #6c63ff 0%,
          #a78bfa 50%,
          #ff6584 100%
        );
        -webkit-background-clip: text;
        -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
        background-clip: text;
        margin-bottom: 16px;
      }
      .hero p {
        font-size: 1rem;
        color: var(--text-muted);
        max-width: 460px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        line-height: 1.7;
      }

      /* Tools */
      .tools {
        padding: 0 24px 72px;
        max-width: 900px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        width: 100%;
      }
      .section-label {
        font-size: 0.82rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        color: var(--text-muted);
        letter-spacing: 1.2px;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
      }
      .grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(260px, 1fr));
        gap: 20px;
      }

      /* Tool card */
      .card {
        background: var(--card);
        border: 1.5px solid var(--card-border);
        border-radius: 24px;
        padding: 28px 24px;
        text-decoration: none;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 12px;
        backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
        -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
        box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(108, 99, 255, 0.1);
        transition: all var(--ease);
        position: relative;
        overflow: hidden;
        color: var(--text);
      }
      .card::before {
        content: "";
        position: absolute;
        inset: 0;
        background: linear-gradient(
          135deg,
          rgba(108, 99, 255, 0.06),
          transparent
        );
        opacity: 0;
        transition: opacity var(--ease);
      }
      .card:not(.dimmed):hover {
        transform: translateY(-6px);
        box-shadow: 0 16px 48px rgba(108, 99, 255, 0.22);
        border-color: rgba(108, 99, 255, 0.35);
      }
      .card:not(.dimmed):hover::before {
        opacity: 1;
      }
      .card.dimmed {
        opacity: 0.58;
        cursor: default;
      }

      .icon {
        font-size: 2.2rem;
        width: 54px;
        height: 54px;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary-light), #ddd6fe);
        border-radius: 16px;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
      }
      .name {
        font-size: 1.05rem;
        font-weight: 700;
      }
      .desc {
        font-size: 0.86rem;
        color: var(--text-muted);
        line-height: 1.6;
        flex: 1;
      }
      .tag {
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        font-size: 0.72rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        padding: 3px 10px;
        border-radius: 100px;
        align-self: flex-start;
      }
      .tag-new {
        background: #dcfce7;
        color: #15803d;
      }
      .tag-soon {
        background: #fef9c3;
        color: #a16207;
      }
      .arrow {
        position: absolute;
        right: 20px;
        top: 50%;
        transform: translateY(-50%);
        font-size: 1.2rem;
        color: var(--primary);
        opacity: 0;
        transition: all var(--ease);
      }
      .card:not(.dimmed):hover .arrow {
        opacity: 1;
        right: 16px;
      }

      /* Footer */
      footer {
        margin-top: auto;
        text-align: center;
        padding: 24px;
        font-size: 0.8rem;
        color: var(--text-faint);
        border-top: 1px solid rgba(108, 99, 255, 0.1);
      }

      @media (max-width: 480px) {
        .hero {
          padding: 52px 16px 36px;
        }
        .tools {
          padding: 0 16px 52px;
        }
        .grid {
          grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="bg">
      <div class="blob blob-1"></div>
      <div class="blob blob-2"></div>
      <div class="blob blob-3"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="wrapper">
      <section class="hero">
        <div class="badge">❖ Maehe Tools</div>
        <h1>子育てを、<br />もっとスマートに。</h1>
        <p>
          習い事・学校・日常のちょっとした手間を省く、便利なツールを集めました。
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="tools">
        <p class="section-label">ツールを選ぶ</p>
        <div class="grid">
          <a class="card" href="/schedule/">
            <div class="icon">📅</div>
            <div class="name">予定インポーター</div>
            <div class="desc">
              LINEメッセージから習い事の予定を自動抽出。ICSファイルでGoogleカレンダーに一括登録できます。
            </div>
            <span class="tag tag-new">✦ NEW</span>
            <span class="arrow">→</span>
          </a>

          <div class="card dimmed">
            <div class="icon">📊</div>
            <div class="name">成長記録</div>
            <div class="desc">
              身長・体重などの成長記録をグラフで可視化。定期的な変化をひと目で確認できます。
            </div>
            <span class="tag tag-soon">準備中</span>
          </div>

          <div class="card dimmed">
            <div class="icon">🚗</div>
            <div class="name">送迎スケジューラー</div>
            <div class="desc">
              複数の子どもの習い事の送迎時間を整理。重複や移動時間をひと目で確認できます。
            </div>
            <span class="tag tag-soon">準備中</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <footer>
        <p>© 2026 Maehe. All rights reserved.</p>
      </footer>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
